fields.description:
Eucalyptus 4.1.2 was developed and tested against NetApp Data ONTAP 8.1.2. With Data ONTAP 8.3.1 Eucalyptus does not correctly detect completion of clone-split operation on NetApp clustered mode SANs resulting in the failure of EBS snapshots and volumes from snapshots. Eucalyptus keys off a string response from ONTAP API which has changed between versions 8.1.2 and 8.3.1. 

Data ONTAP 8.1.2 sends Eucalyptus the following response upon completion of clone split operation 
{noformat}
The volume is not a clone.
{noformat}

Data ONTAP 8.3.1 responds differently
{noformat}
entry doesn't exist
{noformat}
